<subSubSection pageId="0" pageNumber="81" type="description">
<paragraph pageId="0" pageNumber="81">Description.</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="0" pageNumber="81">
Herb, slender, flexible, decumbent and branching stems, with lanceolate leaves 5.0-6.5 
<normalizedToken originalValue="×">x</normalizedToken>
0.4-0.6 cm; strong fibrous root system; pink or purplish flowers.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
